--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
C: change
E: enhancement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 2.0.2 (2020-05-07)
E: Improve Docker support (custom Docker networks)

* Version 2.0.1 (2019-11-17)
E: Minor style improvement

* Version 2.0.0 (2019-10-25)
C: Drop support for CentOS 8 (use 'nftables' role instead)

* Version 1.2.0 (2019-10-18)
F: Add support for CentOS 8

* Version 1.1.0 (2019-05-26)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.8

* Version 1.0.2 (2019-01-01)
E: Minor style improvement

* Version 1.0.1 (2018-12-13)
E: Improve IPv4/IPv6 filters

* Version 1.0.0 (2018-08-02)
F: Remove support for single port rules
F: Add support for multiple ports per rule (multiport/dports)

* Version 0.4.1 (2018-05-31)
E: Correct 'command' variable names

* Version 0.4.0 (2018-05-21)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.5

* Version 0.3.1 (2018-04-24)
E: Improve regular expressions of Docker exceptions

* Version 0.3.0 (2018-04-23)
F: Add rudimentary support for Docker rules and chains

* Version 0.2.0 (2018-03-30)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.4

* Version 0.1.1 (2018-02-16)
F: Fix parameters

* Version 0.1.0 (2018-01-17)
F: Initial release
